%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Manh-5/poem-yLD6zlviNUkRwmmSAfOSjA">Manh 5 - 氓 5</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1ch-D%E1%BB%B1c/T%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%A1n/poem-hnI2KDVcKx_EnfGl94tKmQ">Tân nhạn - 新雁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1ch-D%E1%BB%B1c/author-63sQ6igz79c8AB4tN4pK2g">Quách Dực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Tr%E1%BA%ABm-l%E1%BB%99-4/poem-DUXiqRt3gFqd7O43FnPh2A">Trẫm lộ 4 - 湛露 4</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-h%E1%BA%ADn-ca/poem-NNj51-ebZyApj8ndjN6_VQ">Trường hận ca - 長恨歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br></div>	</div>
